ActDirector of Public Prosecutions Act
PrecisAuthorization of the reappointment for KATHLEEN ROUSSEL of Ottawa, Ontario, Deputy Director of Public Prosecutions, to act as Director of Public Prosecutions, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four months beginning on June 21, 2017, or until a Director of Public Prosecutions is appointed, whichever is earlier.
